{
  "texts": [
    "The application of cutting-edge technologies, including Transformer models and sequence-to-sequence learning in language models, has enabled natural conversations with computers, providing surprisingly good responses.",
    "In computer vision, innovations allow users to create and interact in three dimensions, marking a shift from traditional 2D interactions.",
    "Generative models have opened up new possibilities for users to create images, videos, and audio in ways previously unattainable with conventional tools.",
    "A significant transformation arises from the increasing capabilities of multimodal models, aiming to create a unified model proficient in understanding various modalities and generating diverse modes in context.",
    "Google has introduced a unified language model capable of performing vision, language, question answering, and object detection tasks across more than 100 languages."
  ]
}